Package: soryos-desktop
Version: 0.1.0
Section: metapackages
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: SoryOS Team <maintainers@soryos.local>
Depends: soryos-archive-keyring, sory-shell, sory-theme, sory-settings, sory-installer
Description: SoryOS desktop metapackage
 This metapackage installs the current SoryOS desktop migration modules.
 It is intentionally small and does not remove or replace Pop!_OS packages.
